#Approach:

Max Consecutive Ones – Approach

Array ko traverse karo aur ek counter rakho jo consecutive 1s ko count kare.
Jab bhi 1 mile, counter ko increment karo.
Jab 0 mile, counter ko reset karke 0 kar do kyunki consecutive sequence break ho gaya.

Har step par maximum length update karte raho using max variable.
End me max variable me hi maximum consecutive 1s mil jayenge.

Time Complexity: O(n)
Space Complexity: O(1)

#Code:

class Solution {
    public int findMaxConsecutiveOnes(int[] nums) {
        int maxi = 0;
        int cnt = 0;

        for(int i=0; i<nums.length; i++){
            if(nums[i] == 1){
                cnt++;
                maxi = Math.max(cnt, maxi);
            }
            else{
                cnt = 0;
            }
        }
        return maxi;
    }
}
